      <h2 id="special-thoughts-on-healing-after-losing-a-pet">Special Thoughts on Healing After Losing a Pet</h2>
      <p></p>
<p>The healing process is unique to each individual. These messages offer encouragement and hope for the future.</p>
<p>Losing a pet is a significant loss.  Remember, healing takes time. Allow yourself to grieve, to remember the joy and love your pet brought into your life.  Focus on the happy memories, and know that the love you shared will forever be a part of you.  Surround yourself with those who care, and take the time you need to heal.  Your pet’s memory will continue to inspire and comfort you in the days, weeks, and months ahead.  Their love will remain an enduring part of your heart.</p>
    
  
